{"tid":2056234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"洗忘台灣手足有野想同跟登仔講","createTime":"2020-06-08T13:59:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T16:01:08.000Z","uid":54517,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f328edabebe0d768b12fba57402e3716fca1ccb0","tid":2056234,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:59:16.000Z","msg":"唔知會唔會有連登仔見到我講野,岩岩見到有連登仔話台灣唔駛煩錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你肯定唔知我地已經斷左糧靠自己架啦,個個都係死慳死抵係度捱緊架咋<br />\n唔該唔知就唔好講到我地好好咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者咁講啦 係台灣嘅手足大部分而家係零收入 612都停埋 但係都要食飯㗎<br />\n佢地用緊嘅係之前淨低嘅錢<br />\n我地唔係Ivan ma 我地安份守紀 我地冇食人血 連家長錢都盡量少攞<br />\n望住人地就買100萬台幣錶 我地就食緊20一碗滷肉飯 想我地點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5264ce73487c098a0a78b62deaf6efc087cf226a","tid":2056234,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T14:00:12.000Z","msg":"流亡,SORRY<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70bd626e03551ce16b8e4c92887b017d7b00a4de","tid":2056234,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T14:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75475b798699c1d900dc73ad9e769da2cd396332","tid":2056234,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T14:01:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces